===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*sem-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|som}}, {{m|enm|sum}}, from {{inh|en|ang|sum||some, a certain one}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*sumaz||some, a certain one}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*sem-||one, whole}}. Cognate {{cog|sco|sum}}, {{m|sco|some||some}}, {{cog|frr|som}}, {{m|frr|sam}}, {{m|frr|säm||some}}, {{cog|fy|sommige}}, {{m|fy|somlike||some}}, {{cog|nds|somige||some}}, {{cog|nl|sommige||some}}, {{cog|de|-}} dialectal {{m|de|summige||some}}, {{cog|da|somme||some}}, {{cog|sv|somlig||some}}, {{cog|no|sum}}, {{m|no|som||some}}, {{cog|is|sumur||some}}, {{cog|got|𐍃𐌿𐌼𐍃||one, someone}}. More at {{l|en|same}}.
