===Adverb===
{{en-adv|-}}
# Of a measurement: [[approximately]], [[roughly]].
#: {{syn|en|Thesaurus:approximately}}
#: {{ux|en|I guess he must have weighed '''some''' 90 kilos.}}
#: {{ux|en|'''Some''' 30,000 spectators witnessed the feat.}}
#: {{ux|en|'''Some''' 4,000 acres of land were flooded.}}
# {{lb|en|dialect}} To a certain extent, or for a certain period.
#* '''2014''', C. R. Scott, ''Invisible War: Attack the Covenant''
#*: They walked '''some''' and talked '''some'''.
